<h3 id="overview">Overview</h3>

<p>Care Managers help patients in their care journey by interacting with them using a defined protocol. This helps to keep a check on the patientâ€™s health and allows tracking for the health systems to take the right path.</p>

<h3 id="problem-statement">Problem Statement</h3>

<p>While care managers are completing tasks in the care protocols, they need to access to the patientâ€™s clinical and personal details quite frequently. This leads to them switching tabs and losing the context of the task at hand.</p>
